Every year, the United Nations and other international environmental organizations mark specific days to raise and focus awareness about global issues. These events often act in support of further the UN Sustainable Development Goals. Recognizing and amplifying these events is one way that .eco can act in solidarity with the environmental movement.

Here is the list of event days we will recognize this year. We encourage you to similarly post your support of these initiatives. If there are some important event days that you think we have missed, <a class="chat-link" href="#">please let us know</a>!

